Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在街道边有间茶店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.35,0:00:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好味道！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士大人  运气不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:01:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的丸子的味道可是这条街第一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.92,0:01:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪生意如此兴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.98,0:01:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实因为要给生病的父亲支付药费
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天王寺家欠下了的债务难以还清
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.18,0:01:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咳…  咳…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说  如果到了期限还没有还清
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.71,0:01:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要把我们从这里赶走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天王寺家和地方官是一路人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他仗着官势无理地提高债务的利息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这简直太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.04,0:01:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你们放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.62,0:01:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说我也算是个武士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会保护你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.27,0:01:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真是可靠啊  武士大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小事一桩！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了期限的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样这家店算是完了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  快把借的钱还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求您再宽限几日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.96,0:02:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拿你来抵债吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要带人走的话  就把我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我品味还不至于…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们给我等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我乃花井家当主  花井弥三郎春树
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.36,0:02:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你们的所作所为
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在让我看不下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我以这秘剑…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.89,0:02:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来不像是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天王寺大哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…大…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样！要道歉的话现在还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大  大哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…请问您尊姓大名？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不是役舍丸广事？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:27.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(役舍丸广事是电视剧《三匹斩》中万石的扮演者)
