Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是播磨拳儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢上了我的同学{\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}塚{\r}本天满
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我虽然多次对她进行告白行动  但都以失败告终
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定直求胜负的我却发现了一个冲击性的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是  小满喜欢上了  班上那最呆的怪物乌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说不下去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在绝望之下开始画漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  厄运并没有因此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最敬仰的漫画家二条老师居然就是乌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还被剪掉长胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被剃成秃头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至被误认为和那个金发大小姐坠入爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我最后逃出了日本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海上  我遇到了教导我人生之路的师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海难中存活了下来的我重生了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后回到日本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用他送我的鱼骨笔一直认真画着漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  为了成为真正的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能再度向小满传达我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小奈良
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去给我买个罐装咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  吉田山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好别坐在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦  播磨又不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来  请坐请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了迎接播磨同学特地把凳子先坐热了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我有香蕉  您要吃么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  Thank you  真用心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明马上就要开始文化祭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还给我成天旷课
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到哪里晃去啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小满  你去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨  过来下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊  弦子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校要叫我刑部老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早忘了告诉你  有封给你的明信片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈讲社…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是件苦心等待的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难  难  难道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(恭喜您这次获得特等奖  奖品已经交付寄送  请静待送达)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  新人奖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快趁此机会去告白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪  你究竟在哪  小满
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天满在屋顶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我啊  小满
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  虽然恋爱是个人自由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:41.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云的事  我本来也不想多插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是说是住在莎拉家  其实是和播磨两个人一直待到早上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟  糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的错  使她妹妹陷入窘境
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我也没和乌丸这样过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在和播磨交往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我认为这有点问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  你误解了啊  小满
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹只是为了帮我完成要截稿的漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不得已一晚都和我在一起的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫画的事情又得保密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说八云你很温柔是好  但是的确也太没有防备了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在男孩子眼中看来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让他们觉得你是个  最符合他们口味的百依百顺的女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你一定要小心点！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果播磨同学变得越来越像猴子一样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要对他强硬些！强硬些懂吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要道歉啊  妹妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  {\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}塚{\r}本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨学长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和播磨没关系  别搅进来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我和八云之间的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是太有关系了  我和你妹妹是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香蕉  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为这样就能解决问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有那个想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}塚{\r}本担心的心情我很了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心  你妹妹只不过是在我家待了一晚罢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你住播磨家了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你们顶多就是去餐厅吃饭  或一起骑机车之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  不是我家…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对了！是在弦…在刑部老师的家里！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦子老师家？说谎的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我吧  {\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}塚{\r}本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝对没有做什么不该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着我的眼睛！这像是说谎的人的眼睛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好可爱  小满
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你冒汗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但  但请你相信我  你妹妹绝对没做背叛你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了  我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:09:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}塚{\r}本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会生气只是因为八云没有对我说实话而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不是会令我很寂寞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们毕竟是亲姐妹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了就好  明白了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今开始你们要幸福地生活哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的！我一定会让你妹妹幸福的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～不愧是播磨君！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是靠得住啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下！我说错了…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么会这样——！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳儿  我真的可以收下这个摄像机吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一开始就是这么打算的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然擅自拿别人的名字寄回函卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我没有抽奖运呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有些不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:48.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（恭喜您这次获得特等奖  奖品已经交付寄送  请静待送达\N特等奖品  数码摄像机）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  八云的问题解决了  我也要加油了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又来打扰了～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是文化祭用的服装哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当帅气哦  乌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比之前的姿势更好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:17.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}Tonight search and crazy with Catherine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:23.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}You are everyday everynight shining bright ray
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:28.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}He is like something in the heart alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是帅呆了  乌丸同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从此  登上舞台的我们就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐制作人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说是很棒的乐团所以来看看  结果超出预想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:11:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不想向职业乐坛进军？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真  真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  乌丸同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起出道乐坛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你唱歌和乐器都不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌丸  乌丸同学会去哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会去远方我找不到的地方吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}塚{\r}本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌  乌丸同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唱歌不行  乐器也不会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想多了  就觉得很伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌丸同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出精神来  {\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}塚{\r}本同学一定有{\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}塚{\r}本同学才能办到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我才能办到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龟吉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龟吉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龟吉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龟吉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龟吉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龟吉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龟吉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龟吉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龟吉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龟吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全搞不懂啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「龟吉」是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌丸同学到底想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  这个乌龟到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放弃！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是让我找到只有我才能做的事情的提示！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…龟吉…龟妮…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  这一定是接龙游戏！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龟吉  龟…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:23.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(天满说到没有接上的地方就会爆炸  下同)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没事吧  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龟吉  印度豹  段位差…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过这点小事！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龟吉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶酪蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金刚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚动咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷面！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龟吉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啦啦队女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮盘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪排
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痒痒挠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荨麻疹！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龟吉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九连环
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芥末
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宾戈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝麻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟒蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麝香豌豆花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加香葡萄酒！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么接不下去？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  诅咒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到诅咒就自然会想到睡美人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  乌丸是要我在文化祭出演睡美人！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不明白是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  知道这是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌龟咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌龟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡美人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答对了  真不愧是小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌龟是迟钝的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（迟钝与诅咒音近）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被施以诅咒的就是睡美人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云  便当做好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照姐姐的要求做了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  就麻烦你中午休息的时候送到我的教室里来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦  没关系啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云照我说的做就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我去看乌丸同学的练习了  先走一步啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊  八云
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我给你家里打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才把你留宿播磨学长家的事暴露给你姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是莎拉的错  是我不该说谎的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  多亏了这件事让你们的关系公开了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后就能好好交往了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早  早上好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点古怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽近学姐果然还是喜欢播磨学长的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(午休)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就是文化祭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的文化祭上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要和八云同学共同出演睡美人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.81,0:15:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道的只有花井一个了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道时受到的冲击估计很恐怖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们去吧！到八云同学的身边去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点阻止他为好？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:15:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  花井
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事  周防
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭办的活动是以班级为单位的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.28,0:16:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不可能和她共同演出的  放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要班长的权利在手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点障碍根本算不上什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正只是时间的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  泽近也被轻易地抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是想开点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁  谁被抛弃了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是天满她自己的误会而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是被体育祭上连同腿受伤的自己的份一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带领2-C班走向胜利的播磨同学的气概所感动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一不小心才和他在众人面前大跳土风舞而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你理解就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们理解啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头的时候感觉很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这不是完全不理解吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来  进行准备的半年的确是很长的一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在终于到了实现梦想的时候了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你知道吗？一年级的{\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}塚{\r}本同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  听说是在和二年级的播磨同学交往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是真的——！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可悲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是花井学长的声音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种不好的预感…可是如果不把便当送去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  刚才的叫声是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你参与进去了准没好事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过分！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  今天不吃八云的便当了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云  你真的和播磨…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  {\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}塚{\r}本同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  稻叶同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你点私人问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:18:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在二年级的播磨同学家里留宿的事情是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…啊…嗯  但是那只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我们家八云不是很内向吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是给人添麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨了…不想办法消除误会的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么  四眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨…你这家伙——！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是个莫名其妙的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你搞什么名堂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花井他怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受重创了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了  在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了八云  快把它交给播磨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…啊  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满了八云的爱哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是真的  不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是真的——！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个幸福的家伙  播磨同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年D班来向2年C班发起挑战书了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的文化祭上把一切做个了结吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然冒出来说这种话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭不仅仅是展示  而是战场！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一·条！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来决一胜负吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位都到齐了  很好咧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:17.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(注：西本的口癖为「だす」，译作「咧」)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本日的议题定为分析班上女生的注目点咧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈良训练兵给大家看资料
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数据已传送至各位眼前的电脑上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵯峨野惠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不太熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像中学时期参加过篮球社团
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕由于篮球的关系被期待的腿部曲线不容小觑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是个盲点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈良训练兵  长进不少咧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:21:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结城{\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}紬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:21:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们2-C班唯一一个眼镜娘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.82,0:22:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的  的确是我们班上一个重要的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.49,0:22:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大{\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}塚{\r}舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2-C班的班长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.07,0:22:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据从中学友人那里得来的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她其实是个不为人知的巨乳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难  难道说她正在看着我？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.63,0:22:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}塚{\r}本天…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.47,0:22:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看下一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三原梢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.29,0:22:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2-C班爱打扮的时尚人物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.06,0:22:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据男生中的人气指数推测
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想经验相当丰富
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.63,0:22:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晒成小麦色的健康皮肤和留下的白色泳衣痕迹…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.20,0:22:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队  队长  我已经控制不住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点咧  吉田山伍长  后面还有特别情报
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.02,0:22:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈良训练兵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.06,0:22:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.23,0:22:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刑部弦子老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容貌和身材之优秀已经不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那洋溢的知性可是有着\N在同年级学生中无法感受到飒爽魅力咧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是队长  这些我们都已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.96,0:22:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.96,0:23:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得瞩目之处在此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年长的女教师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个要素相混合  魅力则扩大到无限
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是色情调酒师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  数据正在一点点地被病毒破坏！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.06,0:23:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这里也是  快做数据备份啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.74,0:23:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们重要的数据啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.10,0:23:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！还有一个文件在！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开看看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.13,0:23:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要尽干无聊的事  好好回去学习!  ——刑部弦子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.78,0:23:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.77,0:23:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们班要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？话剧？咖啡厅？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由生存游戏来决定？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.69,0:23:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  Schoo Rumble  2学期
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.73,0:23:55.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,策谋  战场  朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.82,0:23:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经热血澎湃了
